title: Five Unsolved Murders in "The Most Beautiful Small Town in America," Bardstown
itunes:title: Five Unsolved Murders in "The Most Beautiful Small Town in America," Bardstown
description:
Since 2013, there have been four murders and one disappearance in a small Kentucky town. The person who disappeared is presumed dead. Nancy Grace goes in -depth with the producer and co-host of the new podcast "Bardstown," Jessica Noll and investigative reporter Shay McAlister of WHAS
